Package camzup.core

Interface IUtils

All Known Subinterfaces:
ICurve, IEntity, IEntityData, IImaginary, IMaterial, IMatrix, IMesh, IRay, ITransform, IVec
All Known Implementing Classes:
Color, Complex, Curve, Curve2, Curve3, CurveEntity2, CurveEntity3, Entity, Entity2, Entity3, EntityData, Gradient, Imaginary, Mat3, Mat4, Material, MaterialPImage, MaterialSolid, MaterialUv, Matrix, Mesh, Mesh2, Mesh3, MeshEntity2, MeshEntity3, Quaternion, Random, Ray, Ray2, Ray3, Transform, Transform2, Transform3, Utils, Vec, Vec2, Vec3, Vec4
public interface IUtils
Holds mathematical constants used by the rest of the library. Provides convenience functions for printing a hash code and identity hash code as hexadecimal strings.
